divs: Sighting DetailsVery beautiful, and positive frequency from it. Seemed as if they were having fun. Then the spacecraft moved as if it wanted to be seen, was like a dish with top as usually interpreted. Blue lights circulating the dome and every turn a white light sparks, u can clearly see the shape of the objects because how clear it was! The blue was vibrant and different i liked it, im just a young man from baltimore i have a great video i promise on my life i will drop dead right now if im exaggerating anything, i am happy to experience somthing that the WHOLE WORLD is questionable about. Give me a call guys thanks!
